<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="cs">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8" />
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
<title>Hodinový Marek</title>
<style>
  body {
    font-family: "Segoe UI", Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
    margin: 0; padding: 0;
    min-height: 100vh;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    text-align: center;
    transition: background-color 1s, color 1s;
  }
  header {
    padding: 2rem 1rem 1rem;
  }
  h1 {
    margin: 0;
    font-size: 2.5rem;
  }
  section {
    max-width: 600px;
    padding: 1rem 1.5rem 3rem;
  }
  .avatar {
    width: 120px; height: 120px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: #ccc;
    margin: 1rem auto 2rem;
    display: block;
    background-image: url('https://i.pravatar.cc/120?u=hodinovymarek');
    background-size: cover;
    background-position: center;
  }
  a {
    color: inherit;
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: 600;
  }
  a:hover {
    text-decoration: underline;
  }
  footer {
    margin-top: auto;
    padding: 1rem;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: inherit;
  }
  /* Barvy pro období */
  body.spring {
    background: #e6f4ea;
    color: #2a5d34;
  }
  body.spring a {
    color: #a3c55f;
  }
  body.summer {
    background: #d0f0fd;
    color: #045a8d;
  }
  body.summer a {
    color: #f68b1e;
  }
  body.autumn {
    background: #f7ebe1;
    color: #6f3e18;
  }
  body.autumn a {
    color: #d2691e;
  }
  body.winter {
    background: #d9e9f9;
    color: #1b3a6b;
  }
  body.winter a {
    color: #3768b0;
  }
  .contact-info {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    margin-top: 0.5rem;
  }
  .contact-info div {
    margin: 0.3rem 0;
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>
  <header>
    <h1>Hodinový Marek</h1>
    <div class="avatar" aria-label="Profilový obrázek"></div>
  </header>
  <section id="about">
    <h2>O mně</h2>
    <p>Pomáhám s drobnými opravami, údržbou a pracemi v domácnosti a na zahradě.  
    Jsem spolehlivý a vždy připravený pomoci.</p>
  </section>
  <section id="contact">
    <h2>Kontakt</h2>
    <div class="contact-info">
      <div>📞 <a href="tel:+420730648325">730 648 325</a></div>
      <div>✉️ <a href="mailto:marekbala@icloud.com">marekbala@icloud.com</a></div>
      <div>📘 <a href="https://www.facebook.com/markebala" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Facebook Marek Bala</a></div>
    </div>
  </section>
  <footer>
    &copy; 2025 Hodinový Marek
  </footer>

<script>
  function getSeason(date) {
    const month = date.getMonth() + 1;
    if (month >= 3 && month <= 5) return 'spring';
    if (month >= 6 && month <= 8) return 'summer';
    if (month >= 9 && month <= 11) return 'autumn';
    return 'winter';
  }
  document.body.classList.add(getSeason(new Date()));
</script>
</body>
</html>